@startuml IBM_customer-sentiment-on-seller-quality-nlu-cp4d

actor User

participant "Jupyter Notebook" as Notebook
participant "Db2 Database" as DB2
participant "Watson NLU" as NLU
participant "Embedded Dashboard" as Dashboard

User -> Notebook: Execute notebook
activate Notebook

Notebook -> DB2: Load customer review data
activate DB2
DB2 --> Notebook: Return raw data
deactivate DB2

loop for each review
    Notebook -> NLU: Send review text
    activate NLU
    NLU --> Notebook: Return sentiment and emotion analysis
    deactivate NLU
end

Notebook -> Notebook: Calculate seller ratings

Notebook -> Dashboard: Update with processed data
activate Dashboard

User -> Dashboard: View seller quality insights
Dashboard --> User: Display interactive visualizations

deactivate Dashboard
deactivate Notebook

@enduml